Architecture with Notification Service
Booking Service
    ↓ publishes event to Kafka
    booking.created topic
    vehicle.exit topic
        ↓
Notification Service (consumes)
    ↓
Sends HTML email via Gmail SMTP
This way Booking Service doesn't need to know about emails at all — fully decoupled.

